description: 2015 CONSTRUCTION - Located just one block from West Broadway shops and restaurants...The Residences at Dahlgren Hall feature 18 newly constructed condominium homes. This two bedroom Residence features: open concept kitchen/living/dining, hardwood flrs throughout, master en suite w/walk in custom closet, private outdoor space, deeded storage room in basement & GARAGE PARKING. The custom kitchen showcases solid wood painted cabinetry, Thermador & Bosch appliances w/ granite countertops with waterfall detail on island/peninsula. Sonos sound system with mult zones and Bluetooth capability add to the appeal of this unit. Energy conscious features include exterior Hardie plank and PVC trim, tankless hot water heater, high eff heating and cooling & Marvin low e windows.  Elevator building.  Amazing common roof terrace with city views & multiple seating areas and club room make this a fabulous place to live!  PHOTOS ARE OF MODEL UNIT AND ARE REPRESENTATIVE OF THE FINISHES THROUGHOUT THE BUILDING.
